{"tid":1022535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放生變殺生 　「佛光普照」海龜一死一重傷","createTime":"2019-02-15T05:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T07:03:07.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"24bd91a47ff2f8757341013b72f33fc12fe3c04e","tid":1022535,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190215/photo/bkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190215114437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190215114437&h=ed7104d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190215/photo/bkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190215114437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190215114437&h=6c5461f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宗教人士在大時大節都會聚集「放生」動物，不過就被批評自私兼「殺生」。日前有釣魚客在蒲台島附近水域發現海面「有嘢浮吓浮吓」，駛近才發現是一隻受了傷，背殻被人用油漆寫上「放生」的海龜；亦有志願團體在屯門清理沙灘垃圾時，發現一隻背殻寫有「佛光普照」的海龜，可惜已無生命迹象。漁護署救在其社交網站再次呼籲市民，放生前要先諗一諗，「愛佢唔好害佢」，以免放生變成往生。<br />\n<br />\n事發昨日（14日）下午約5時，市民Alan Tam與外甥釣魚回程途中，在蒲台島附近水域發現一隻受傷海龜在水面掙扎。「海龜殻已經畀螺旋槳打爆，右尾腿都撥唔到水，背殻仲寫住『放生』兩字！」Alan將海龜救起，再帶到水警基地，並謂「希望海龜平安無事」。另外，非政府組織Plastic Free Seas前日（13日）在屯門淨灘時，發現一隻已死亡的懷疑水龜，背殻被人用白色油漆寫上「佛光普照」。其頭部伸出，部分甲殻亦已脫落。有網民留言稱，該隻「放生」屬淡水龜，「淡水龜放落海放生，唔死至怪！」<br />\n<br />\n漁護署昨晚在社交網站發文指，受傷的海龜為成年雌性綠海龜，甲背有一道長約35厘米，懷疑被撞擊造成的傷痕。其體重只有56公斤，嚴重過輕，現已在海洋公園接受治療。漁護署續提醒市民，不恰當放生動物容易導致牠們死亡，更會影響本地生態平衡。「放生前，諗清楚係咪真係可以令動物幸福快樂！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190215/bkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190215%2Fbkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001.html&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=de716819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190215/bkn-20190215110407854-0215_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"781feab00f62634bba7956033c4c9853a8b252c0","tid":1022535,"uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"放生撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有單放生毒蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e20486823425fa1814f86a5b7065efcfd4debab","tid":1022535,"uid":158411,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2603/2603878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2603%2F2603878.jpg&h=4111fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c11ca8b0ed8f69d4f476aae0766e865754747268","tid":1022535,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"人類總要"},{"pid":"c4b0203f8aac581fe35b69cd60486bc11e531dcc","tid":1022535,"uid":55597,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"放生係偽善行為"},{"pid":"def8b8f898e9333f9e5a2bc4477cb8974dea1650","tid":1022535,"uid":71133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"睇字都想像到班廢中放生完戴光環好撚滿足嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1758ad14ada51724e135afd099785d8d6f260b6f","tid":1022535,"uid":163801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"你睇吓隻海龜幾可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保撚 vs 放生撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4225acfb6e8fd660cacceff1c60ae6d402ed77d3","tid":1022535,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：佛光普